Class HnswGraphBuilder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.util.hnsw.HnswGraphBuilder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of vector
    public final class HnswGraphBuilder<T>

      • build

        public OnHeapHnswGraph build​(RandomAccessVectorValues<T> vectorsToAdd)
                      throws IOException
        Reads all the vectors from two copies of a RandomAccessVectorValues. Providing two copies enables efficient retrieval without extra data copying, while avoiding collision of the returned values.
        Parameters:
        vectorsToAdd - the vectors for which to build a nearest neighbors graph. Must be an independent accessor for the vectors
        Throws:
        IOException
